item.title: React Native bridge for iOS Health Kit
item.description: React Native bridge for iOS Health Kit. It enabled React Native apps to subscribe Health Kit data updates. This project was particularly difficult on receiving the updates from Health Kit while the app was on the background. It was a interesting challenge to orchestrate the timing of life cycles between iOS and React Native layers
